content.original: Pressurized Canister containing Acid for the Fluid gun, weakening a targets Armor Drastically. On a Critical Hit, the Pressurized Container will explode dealing damage to the install location. Risk can be mitigated with the use of C.A.S.E.
content.prevOriginal: Pressurized Canister containing Acid for the Fluid gun, weakening a targets Armor Drastically. On a Critical Hit, the Pressurized Container will explode dealing damage to the install location. Risk can be mitigated with the use of C.A.S.E.
content.content: 装有液体喷枪用的酸液加压罐,大大削弱了目标的装甲.当受到严重损伤时,高压容器会爆炸,对安装部位造成伤害.使用C.A.S.E.可以降低风险.

content.original: Pressurized Canister containing Inferno for the Fluid gun, coating the Target in burning Chemicals. On a Critical Hit, the Pressurized Container will explode dealing damage to the install location. Risk can be mitigated with the use of C.A.S.E.

content.content: 装有液体喷枪用的炼狱化合物加压罐,让燃烧的化合物覆盖目标.当受到严重损伤时,高压容器会爆炸,对安装部位造成伤害.使用C.A.S.E.可以降低风险.

content.original: Pressurized Canister containing Oil for the Fluid gun, impairing a Targets Stability and Movement. It's also flammable. On a Critical Hit, the Pressurized Container will explode dealing damage to the install location. Risk can be mitigated with the use of C.A.S.E.

content.content: 装有液体喷枪用的油液加压罐,损害目标的稳定性和移动能力.它也是易燃的.当受到严重损伤时,高压容器会爆炸,对安装部位造成伤害.使用C.A.S.E.可以降低风险.

On a Critical Hit, the Pressurized Container will explode dealing damage to the install location. Risk can be mitigated with the use of C.A.S.E.
